WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:05.000
This six year old is finally ready to compete.

2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
His opponent is a bigger, stronger, eight year old ram.

3
00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:31.000
The challenger must provoke the fight.

4
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:38.000
With body kicks and tongue flicking he taunts his opponent.

5
00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:58.000
The older ram seems to walk away in submission.

6
00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:10.000
But his posture is known as the low stretch.
It means, "You wanna piece of me? Come get it."

7
00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:47.000
The force of the impact, delivered at 35 km/h, is enough to kill a human, instantly.

8
00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:56.500
Two layers of skull protect their brains.

9
00:01:56.500 --> 00:02:00.000
The fight lasts for hours.
Each Ram battering the other, dozens of times.

